import React from 'react'; import './AboutMe.css'; import { useLanguage } from '../contexts/LanguageContext'; const AboutMe: React.FC = () => { const { t } = useLanguage(); return (
{t.aboutMe.label}

{t.aboutMe.paragraph1}
